articles.title: Kansas put abortion rights on the ballot. The surprising outcome is reverberating across the United States - ABC News
articles.description: In the first electoral test of Americans' mood since the US Supreme Court reversed Roe v Wade, a traditionally conservative state votes to protect abortion rights. It could be a sign of what's to come.
